message.content:
Tēnā koe! Kei te pai. Ka whakapau kaha ahau ki te āwhina i a koe ki ēnei whakararuraru. Hei whakapau kaha i tēnei tino whakamahi, tukuna mai ngā whakapākehā, ā, ka whakakorengia e ahau ngā whakapākehā.

1. Ki te whakatārewatanga i tētahi taupānga pūkoro, whakararuraru, whakatāwheratia te taupānga i te waho o te pūkoro.
2. Whakararuraru i te pūkoro.
3. Whakauru ki roto i te taupānga.
4. Whakararuraru i ngā whakararuraru katoa e whai ake nei:
   - Whakararuraru i ngā āpure (settings) o te taupānga. Ka whiwhi i ngā whakararuraru mō te pūkoro me te whakakore i ētahi āpure e whakaaetia ana ki te whakatārewatanga pūkoro.
   - Whakararuraru i ngā whakaputanga (notifications) o te taupānga. Ka whiwhi i ngā whakararuraru mō te pūkoro me te whakakore i ngā whakaputanga e whakaaetia ana ki te whakatārewatanga pūkoro.
   - Whakararuraru i ngā āpitihanga (permissions) o te taupānga. Ka whiwhi i ngā whakararuraru mō te pūkoro me te whakakore i ngā āpitihanga e whakaaetia ana ki te whakatārewatanga pūkoro.
   - Whakararuraru i ngā whakararuraru o te pūkoro i roto i te taupānga. Ka whiwhi i ngā whakar
